      "content": "exactly. it feels so much more honest than trying to fight to \"recover.\" people always talk about getting better, but maybe for someone like me, there isn't a \"better\" version to go back to. maybe the truth is just that some people are meant to be broken. it's just so heavy to keep trying when the end result is always the same.",
